<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Service Agreement</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px; /* Ensure it's not too wide */
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      h1,
      h2 {
        color: #000000;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .details,
      .terms,
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #999;
      }

      /* Button Styles */
      .custom-button {
        min-width: 150px;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: black;
        background-color: #fbce44; /* colorScheme equivalent */
        border: 2px solid black;
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 5px;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .call {
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;

        width: 20%;
      }

      .custom-button:hover {
        background-color: #f5b642; /* Hover state */
      }

      .header-logo {
        width: 20%;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header-container">
        <img
          class="header-logo"
          src="https://assets.zyrosite.com/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,w=400,fit=crop,q=95/Yanzgg1xJeiNVanE/loading...-mjE911qvjLs7gkNX.png"
          alt="Company Logo"
        />
        <h3><%= subject %></h3>
      </header>

      <div class="row">
        <h5>Hi <%= first %></h5>
        <p>
          you just signed a new service agreement with <%+ providerName %> for
          <%= product.name %>. We've attached a copy for your records and
          included those who need to know about the agreement.
        </p>
        <p><%+ providerName %> has also been sent a copy.</p>
        <h4>Service Agreements</h4>
        <p>
          Service agreements help you know the price and conditions of the
          service you get. They keep you and your providers on the same page and
          help you both out when things get muddled.
        </p>
        <h4>With Circle</h4>
        <p>
          Getting free service agreements from any of your providers is quick
          and easy. Head to the website to get started.
        </p>

        <div class="call">
          <a href="http://circleindependent.com/start" class="custom-button">
            Start
          </a>
        </div>
        <p>Have a great day.</p>
        <br />
        <h5>Circle Team</h5>
        <br />
      </div>

      <section class="details service"></section>

      <div class="row"></div>

      <div class="footer">
        <img
          class="footer-logo"
          width="5%"
          src="../../client/public/logo.png"
        />
        &copy; 2024 Circle Independent. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://assets.zyrosite.com/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,w=400,fit=crop,q=95/Yanzgg1xJeiNVanE/loading...-mjE911qvjLs7gkNX.png"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
